Instructions for Intalling on EngineYard Cloud (EC2)

Settings:

ruby 1.8.7
rails 2.3.4

Unix packages:

freeimage
ffmpeg
rabbitmq-server
xorg-x11 (for cutycapt)
Not sure about these: libxml2-dev, libxslt-dev, readline-devel, curl-devel

Gems:
bundler 0.9.25
jeweler 1.4.0+
daemons 1.0.9+

Filesystem:

symlink ffmpeg to /usr/local/bin/ffmpeg

Security:

Add firewall opening to AMQP port (specify source networks)
